Package ys.succinct.xml.dom

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    OffsetStore
    A store for the character content that can be read by the known offset.
    OrderedStore
    An ordered store of the character content.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractCharacterData
    A succinct node that implements the common CharacterData API.
    AbstractReadonlyNode
    An abstract node that implements Node API that is common to the read-only nodes of the succinct DOM.
    AbstractSuccinctNode
    A succinct representation of Node that is identified by its position(s) in the SuccinctDom.
    ArrayOffsetStore
    A simple OffsetStore that is backed by the character array and stores the content as is.
    ArrayOffsetStore.Builder
    A builder that helps to construct a ArrayOffsetStore.
    AttributeImpl
    A succinct Attr node.
    AttributeMapImpl
    A map-like collection of the attribute nodes of the element that are available lazily.
    AttributeTextImpl
    A Text node that belongs to the attribute and represents its character value.
    CDataImpl
    A succinct CDATASection node.
    CommentImpl
    A succinct Comment node.
    DocumentContext
    An object that holds the properties of the XML document like the XML declaration, URI, etc.
    DocumentImpl
    A succinct Document node.
    ElementImpl
    A succinct Element node.
    ElementStore
    An ordered store of the information about the following types of the XML nodes: Node.DOCUMENT_NODE Node.ELEMENT_NODE Node.COMMENT_NODE Node.CDATA_SECTION_NODE.
    ElementStore.Builder
    A builder that helps to construct an ElementStore.
    FixedNodeList
    An ordered collection of known Nodes.
    NameStore
    An ordered store for the family of the XML names.
    NameStore.Builder
    A builder that helps to construct a NameStore.
    NodeListImpl
    An ordered collection of the succinct Nodes that are available lazily.
    ProcessingInstructionImpl
    A succinct ProcessingInstruction node.
    QNameStore
    An ordered store of the information about the qualified names of the XML nodes.
    QNameStore.Builder
    A builder that helps to construct a QNameStore.
    SuccinctDom
    An object that contains all the succinct data structures to support DOM API.
    TextImpl
    A succinct Text node.
    ValueStore
    An ordered store for the XML text content (node values).
    ValueStore.Builder
    A builder that helps to construct a ValueStore.
